	<h1>Welcome to Stoneship</h1>

	<p>Stoneship is the personal web site of Denis Defreyne, a 21-year old student, web designer and developer from Scheldewindeke, Belgium.</p>

	<p>Here's the latest journal entry I've written, for you to read:</p>

